&gt; in
&gt; &gt; order to rule out any possible suspicion of manipulation. You can 
&gt; for
&gt; &gt; instance increase the volume or dynamics of an entire clip 
&gt; (including
&gt; &gt; the experimenter&#39; s voice), filter or denoise it to make it 
&gt; clearer, but
