&gt; match
&gt; &gt; with what it &quot;should be&quot;. At least, the unedited version should 
&gt; always
&gt; &gt; be provided along with the edited version.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; But that&#39;s only my personal opinion which I thought I had to 
&gt; express, as
&gt; &gt; we should always be able to present our results to a critical 
&gt; public.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Stefan
